</a><br/><br/>Jayne is a photographer that has swallowed her pride and is trying to get a photo of the recluse sculptor, R S Morgan. Traveling to Maine to find her photo muse for a tabloid magazine, Jayne steps into one mess after another after meeting Reed Kimball, a single father and a retired cop.<br/><br/><a href='http://s945.photobucket.com/user/jamielk32/media/Mobile%20Uploads/PicsArt_06-05-06.50.46_zpsvosphl47.jpg.html' target='_blank' rel='nofollow noopener'>
