</a><br><br><b>
  <i>"His need to hold her, to mark her, to become part of her, was primitive, as demanding as the need to take his next breath. </i>
</b><br><br>The present fight for survival mixed with a past of secrets and devastation, Reed and Jayne take us in whirlwind battle against the evil after them and the ones they love.<br><br>◇◇◇◇◇◇◇◇◇◇◇◇◇◇◇◇◇◇◇<br><br>My favorite kind of book!! Suspenseful, thrilling, sexually charged page turner that leaves you NEEDING to know what is going to happen!!!<br><br>Not only are the MC'S easy to love by the supporting characters are awesome and we know they have their own stories! <br><br><br>Perfect Miss Leigh!!! Book 2....I can't wait!!</span>
